posting_body: ["EAST BOCA RATON, this property sits in an '''A Rated'' School Zone in Palm Beach Farms and close to the Florida Atlantic University.", 'Huge Corner Lot - 5 bedrooms, 3 full baths with bright open floor plan.', 'New kitchen with quartz countertop and stainless appliances.', 'Large outdoor patio with pool.', 'M/Bedroom opens to the pool as well.', 'Home have been all completed remodeled, new roof, all Impact window/doors, Yard is all fenced in, with Big Pool Patio and outdoor kitchen (countertop stove and refrigerator); perfect for outdoor entertainment.', 'Patio pool surrounded by lush greenery and tropical fruit trees (avocadoes, mangoes, starfruit, bananas).', 'Huge paved front yard with circular driveway.', 'Driving minutes to great restaurants, Boca beaches, historic downtown, the luxury landmark (Mizner Park)', 'Contact us to schedule a tour today.', 'Please TEXT me your NAME and', 'AD REFERENCE', 'below and We will contact you ASAP.', 'Book your appointment online today!', 'ANNUAL RENTALS ONLY.', 'Ad Reference:', 'RX10821776', 'Text at:', 'show contact info', 'Ask for ANDREW', 'Availability can change daily, If this rental is not available or isn’t the property for you, Text me or call me and We will help you find the right residence for you.', 'We have rentals all over Palm Beach and Broward County!']
